    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Tamás Nádasdy (Prague, 11 April 1549)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">1. He recently received his letter, together with the
                            letters addressed to Hofmann and Guzman. In his letter he asks Oláh to
                            intervene with the King on the issue of redeeming the Sopron tithe,
                            which he has done, and he will learn from the King’s letter what he has
                            accomplished. 2. Stepan has returned from Constantinople and has brought
                            with him István Majláth’s letter to Nádasdy, which he is attaching. If
                            Majláth is well and there is hope for his release, Nádasdy should let
                            him know. He recommends the Eger affairs to his attention and is
                            awaiting his instructions as to what he should do. He has reminded Hans
                            Hofmann to respond to Nádasdy, to which he said that he had already done
                            so and would write again.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Servitiorum meorum commendationem, Spectabilis et Magnifice Domine
                    et Frater Observandissime!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">[1.] Litteras,<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1">We do not know
                        this letter.</note> quas Dominatio Vestra Magnifica ex
                        <placeName>Diozeg</placeName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.2"
                        >Sládkovičovo.</note> decima quarta Martii ad me dedit, <del
                        corresp="Olahus">nudiustertius</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">ante
                        dies aliquot</add> accepi unacum litteris ad dominos
                        <persName>Hoffmanum</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.3">Hans
                        Hofmann, see Ep. 347. Cap. 5.</note> et <persName>Guzmanum</persName>,<note
                        type="critic" xml:id="note.4">Márton Guzman occurs in the correspondence of
                        Antal Verancsics and Tamás Nádasdy.</note> quas illis reddidi. In litteris,
                    quas ad me dedit, rogavit me, ut apud <persName>maiestatem regiam</persName>,
                    dominum nostrum clementissimum pro annuentia et permissione redemptionis decimae
                    Soproniensis intercederem. Feci, quod mihi Dominatio Vestra Magnifica mandavit,
                    et non aliter, quam in re mea, diligentiam omnem praestiti. Effecissemque nunc
                    quoque, si Dominatio Vestra Magnifica tardius, quam opus erat, voluntatem suam
                    non significasset, verum quid maiestas sua regia responderit, Dominatio Vestra
                    Magnifica ex litteris eiusdem intellegit. Ego deinceps quoque post maiestatem
                    regiam faciam omnia in re Dominationis Vestrae Magnificae diligenter modo, quid
                    praestare possum. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">[2.] <persName>Stepan</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.5"
                        >We do not know him more closely.</note> ex
                        <placeName>Constantinopoli</placeName> his diebus reversus huc venit et
                    attulit litteras has praesentibus adiunctas domini
                        <persName>Maylath</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.6">István
                        Majláth.</note> ad Dominationem Vestram Magnificam datas, quas nunc eidem
                    mitto. Si frater ille noster bene valet, et liberationis suae spem facit
                    aliquam, Dominatio Vestra Magnifica faciat me certiorem.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">Agriensia mea negotia Dominationi Vestrae Magnificae commendo, et
                    rogo, ut dum revertetur divino auxilio, me de singulis edoceat, quae ibi fiant.
                    Et si spes est aliqua pecuniae illinc mihi <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert"
                        >nunc</add> exspectandae in his meis maximis expensis.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">Dominum <persName>Hofmanum</persName> admonui, ut responderet; dixit
                    se iam scripsisse Dominationi Vestrae Magnificae et adhuc scribere velle. Quod
                    reliquum est, Dominationem Vestram Magnificam feliciter valere opto, <milestone
                        unit="pb"/>ut fratrem optimum.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.6">Ex <placeName>Praga</placeName> undecima Aprilis anno 1549. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.7">
                    <seg type="signature">Servitor et frater Agriensis etc.</seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.8">Ad manus spectabilis et magnifici domini Thomae Nadasdi perpetui
                    comitis terrae Fogaras etc. domini et fratris observandissimi.</p>
            </div>
